#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn15.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Sukhitasutta "
msgstr "12. In a Good Way "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.187, sc1
msgctxt "sn15.12:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.12:1.2"
msgid "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro … pe … "
msgstr "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning. … "

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.3"
msgid "yaṃ, bhikkhave, passeyyātha sukhitaṃ susajjitaṃ, niṭṭhamettha gantabbaṃ: "
msgstr "When you see someone in a good way, in a happy state, you should conclude: "

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.4"
msgid "‘amhehipi evarūpaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ iminā dīghena addhunā’ti. "
msgstr "‘In all this long time, we too have undergone the same thing.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.12:1.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.6"
msgid "Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro. "
msgstr "Transmigration has no known beginning. … "

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.7"
msgid "Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn15.12:1.8"
msgid "alaṃ vimuccitun”ti. "
msgstr "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.12:1.9"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
